1. Duration of use  
   Describes how long the reviewer has used the product.
2. Observed effects  
   Notes specific changes or improvements after use.
3. Application method  
   Explains the technique used to apply the product.
4. Scent description  
   Provides details about the fragrance quality or type.
5. Reaction to skin  
   Discusses how the product interacts with skin conditions.
6. Packaging satisfaction  
   Expresses opinions on the product's packaging design.
7. Popularity feedback  
   Mentions comments or compliments received from others.
8. Layering suggestions  
   Advises on combining products for enhanced results.
9. Emotional impact  
   Reflects feelings associated with using the product.
10. Price perception  
   Discusses perceived value relative to product quality.
